Package javafe.genericfile

Interface Summary
GenericFile A GenericFile is a least-common-denominator representation of a read-only file (or directory).
 

Class Summary
NormalGenericFile A NormalGenericFile represents a normal file (File) as a GenericFile.
UnopenableFile Instances of UnopenableFile are GenericFiles that cannot be opened.
ZipGenericFile A ZipGenericFile represents a zipfile-entry file (java.util.zip.ZipEntry) as a GenericFile.
